Author: wheresmywinegums
Text: I feel the same way, OP. I’ve lowkey wanted to die for the last 7 years. Humanity is a huge letdown and most days I just don’t have the energy to live. The guilt over food and my body just makes it even worse. Black coffee, good books, and my boyfriend are my only guilt-free pleasures, but sometimes that doesn’t seem like enough to keep living. I try to fight those dark thoughts with every ounce of rationality and self-preservation I have.

Author: danithegreatish
Text: it’s going to be alright, i promise there is hope! there’s a lot of bad but there’s also so many people trying and doing good. there is light! i promise
